show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/FkXeTv
show.description: Poor Bihar student Vikram "Bicky" Jha enters elite college on sports scholarship. He falls for wealthy Kishika Ambani, who uses him then marries another for business. Heartbroken, Bicky quits sports and focuses on education. Years later, English teacher Preeti helps him secure educational grants. Kishika returns dying, reveals their son Arav. Bicky becomes Sports Minister, marries Preeti, and raises Arav.
